      -- hz : z ‚ąą Set.univ.pi A means ‚ąÄ i, z i ‚ąą A i
      -- We need to show x = (y, z) ‚ąą ‚ÜĎ(Fintype.piFinset F) ‚ÄĘ Set.univ.pi A
      -- This means we need to find h ‚ąą Fintype.piFinset F and k ‚ąą Set.univ.pi A such that x = h ‚ÄĘ k
